<paragraph id="4556F7974FA8BCED82DB0502332B33CE" pageId="0" pageNumber="339">K 1536, Thailand, Pai, on twigs of an undetermined dicotyledonous tree, 13.XI.2019, I.A. Gavrilov-Zimin.</paragraph>
